# WatchAgent Testing Policy

When adding or modifying behavior:

- Add deterministic unit tests.
- Tests must not depend on live Open-Meteo data.
- Tests that touch PostgreSQL must use the clean_db fixture.
- Classifier tests should use controlled fake readings.
- Poller tests should mock fetch_current_weather().
- API tests should validate response shape, not just status codes.
- Event detection tests should include both positive and negative cases.
- Run pytest before committing.